{"tid":414970,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"窮JJ供部Macbook定上Carousell買部二手機好？","createTime":"2017-09-26T15:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T23:25:41.000Z","uid":148233,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ca0ed74304428b292e8df16ccb35dfdf9c16569c","tid":414970,"uid":148233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:13:28.000Z","msg":"如題，小弟想要部手提平時做用黎做下功課同做Project咁。<br />\n自己就傾向買部二手頂住檔先，因為見到二手網有d Macbook機都唔錯，價錢4000～5000都可以接受到，但係要Full pay，冇保養（不過要同屋企人借錢）<br />\n咁屋企人就係都話唔好上網買，驚俾人呃，又冇保養乜乜乜...話幫我供部新機好過，雖然分期俾，一個月俾700蚊睇落唔多，但係圍返都好乸利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有d肉赤（d錢最後我都係要逐個月還俾屋企人）<br />\n究竟Full pay買平價二手Macbook（冇保養）<br />\n定貴價買部新機（有保養）好呢？求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9edf67d93b01fa42cec7df04e139829360e914ed","tid":414970,"uid":126388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:16:34.000Z","msg":"讀書就二手啦 依個價錢買到部性能好啲既機 <br />\n讀完書賣番都唔洗蝕<br />\n利申 過來人"},{"pid":"665b31a0c6aedee0fa080f9947e9d2be0c3cf064","tid":414970,"uid":117032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:17:38.000Z","msg":"卑撚心機讀好啲書儲錢買過部新啦<br />\n部MBA用撚左我5年都未壞"},{"pid":"cfdcda69139a0cc577ca1db014d609df7216e9a6","tid":414970,"uid":62167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:19:39.000Z","msg":"根本唔需要 唔好買"},{"pid":"8407e198baa75eb1bc20402eb5a7830e4bbc0f1a","tid":414970,"uid":36895,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:20:51.000Z","msg":"dcfever &gt; carosell"},{"pid":"d9e34155e2a282c229e13988549f012ec03ea4b0","tid":414970,"uid":148233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:23:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本唔需要 唔好買</blockquote><br />\n做功課超級唔方便，我初初都諗住唔買，用手機算。當我做完第一份功課先知有部手提嘅好處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc79c7bd9e31c7dcc7b6668c980e1b9b1630a5a8","tid":414970,"uid":148233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB